{"id":28686,"title":"Use of naltrexone in ketamine dependence.","abstract":"Ketamine is used as a cheap alternative to anaesthetic agents in developing countries. It is also misused as a rave drug because of its psychedelic effect. There are no guidelines for effective management of ketamine withdrawal effects or dependence. Herein we report a case of ketamine dependence and its successful treatment with opioid receptor antagonist naltrexone. ","date":"2014-05-19","categories":"Chemically-Induced Disorders","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24813545","annotations":[{"name":"Ketamine","weight":0.906012,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ketamine"},{"name":"Naltrexone","weight":0.889412,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naltrexone"},{"name":"Opioid","weight":0.821773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opioid"},{"name":"Receptor (biochemistry)","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Receptor_(biochemistry)"},{"name":"Anesthetic","weight":0.779953,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anesthetic"},{"name":"Receptor antagonist","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Receptor_antagonist"},{"name":"Opioid receptor","weight":0.69893,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opioid_receptor"},{"name":"Withdrawal","weight":0.678276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Withdrawal"},{"name":"Drug","weight":0.678276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drug"},{"name":"Substance dependence","weight":0.621052,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substance_dependence"},{"name":"Developing country","weight":0.519526,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Developing_country"},{"name":"Psychedelic","weight":0.493499,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychedelic"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.453863,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Rave","we